      <title>Reolink Trackmix PoE camera review - Customer service needs improvement 🤬</title>
      <dc:creator><![CDATA[Nico]]></dc:creator>
      <description>
      <![CDATA[
      <p>Testing and integrating the Reolink Trackmix PoE camera with Frigate and Home Assistant, and a rant against the brand&apos;s customer service 👎</p><picture>
  <source srcset="https://haade.fr/assets/images/generated/posts/174/test-camera-reolink-trackmix-poe-top-product-poor-aftersale-720-e8505fd08.webp 720w" type="image/webp">
