</picture>

      <p>I recently purchased a Reolink Trackmix PoE camera to equip my home and ordered directly from the official Reolink website, Reolink.com. However, I wanted to cancel the order because I have another camera that’s more suitable (smaller size), but the cancellation process with Reolink wasn’t handled correctly.
</p>
      <p>Read the full article: <a href="https://haade.fr/en/blog/test-and-integration-camera-reolink-trackmix-poe-frigate-homeassistant">Reolink Trackmix PoE camera review - Customer service needs improvement 🤬</a> on the blog <a href="https://haade.fr/en/">Haade.fr</a>.</p>
